python-signalfd

Python bindings to the Linux signalfd library/system call

This version is by Jean-Paul Calderone, with extensions by Michael
Schurter.  More info and links to original sources:

https://launchpad.net/python-signalfd
https://code.launchpad.net/~schmichael/python-signalfd/helpers
http://blog.schmichael.com/2011/02/20/signalfd/
